    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve totally babied it from day one! It looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor. There's not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is still smelling fresh and spotless. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I\u2019m looking for a quick sale to a good home. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
