    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve treated it like a member of the family\u2014always garaged and kept in showroom condition! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot, with that fresh car smell and a finish that shines like a mirror. I'm honestly a bit heartbroken to let it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
